# Progress UI for Sliding Window Processing

## Overview

When processing large documents (>512 tokens) with the sliding window approach, the UI now shows real-time progress updates to keep users informed.

---

## What Users See

### Small Documents (≤512 tokens)

**Progress Message:**
```
Processing document...
```

**Duration:** <1 second

---

### Large Documents (>512 tokens)

#### Phase 1: Initial Message
```
Processing large document: 7 chunks (2871 tokens)
```

#### Phase 2: Chunk Processing (with percentage)
```
Processing chunk 1/7 (14%)...
Processing chunk 2/7 (29%)...
Processing chunk 3/7 (43%)...
Processing chunk 4/7 (57%)...
Processing chunk 5/7 (71%)...
Processing chunk 6/7 (86%)...
Processing chunk 7/7 (100%)...
```

#### Phase 3: Merging Results
```
Merging results (found 167 entities)...
```

#### Phase 4: Completion
```
Completed: 142 unique entities detected
```

---

