## Summary

✅ **Implementation complete**
- Progress callback added to `predict()` method
- UI updates every chunk with percentage
- Merging step shows entity count
- Completion message shows final count

✅ **User-friendly**
- Clear messages about what's happening
- Real-time progress updates
- Percentage shows how far along
- No silent waiting periods

✅ **Backward compatible**
- progressCallback is optional
- Existing code works unchanged
- New code can leverage progress updates

✅ **Ready to test**
- Reload extension
- Upload any large file
- Watch progress updates in UI

